<h1>{import_wizard} Import to Media Gallery Wizard</h1>
Please enter the directory that is the Coppermine root.
This directory must be the <b>absolute</b> path on your server, meaning the full path from the root directory.
This directory will have subdirectories such as <b>include</b> and <b>albums</b>.
<p>
<form method="post" action="{form_action}">
<fieldset style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #000000">
	<br>
	<legend>Import Wizard</legend><br><br>
	<label for="configdir">Coppermine Root Directory:&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
	      <input type="text" name="configdir" size="80">
		  <br><br>
</fieldset>
<div style="text-align:center;">
            <input type="submit" value="next"   name="mode" />
            <input type="submit" value="cancel" name="mode" />
</div>
</form>